EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
DNC 19.
1. GUNNERY EXERCISES 0900Z TO 1800Z DAILY
   28 FEB THRU 04 MAR IN AREA WITHIN 27 MILES
   OF 57-38.2N 009-53.2W. VESSELS INTENDING
   TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 OR
